&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Liberation Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium;"&gt;19/08 - &lt;a href="/debian-ba" style="color: #559900; text-decoration: underline;"&gt;Salvador - Bahia&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
